That's true, Siri.

839
00:42:17,480 --> 00:42:18,760
So you agree now?

840
00:42:18,760 --> 00:42:19,960
I must tilt the table the other way around.

841
00:42:19,960 --> 00:42:21,120
That's not it!

842
00:42:21,120 --> 00:42:22,720
It's alright. I'll have someone fix it tomorrow.

843
00:42:22,800 --> 00:42:23,600
Hey!

844
00:42:25,160 --> 00:42:26,320
It's already broken, ma'am.

845
00:42:26,560 --> 00:42:28,760
Nevermind, Kreetha.

846
00:42:29,000 --> 00:42:31,520
Ma'am, it took me so long to get the information.

847
00:42:31,520 --> 00:42:32,880
It was very hard.

848
00:42:33,640 --> 00:42:34,640
It's alright.

849
00:42:35,200 --> 00:42:37,200
I got help.

850
00:42:42,880 --> 00:42:45,640
And here he is. He's a life saver.

851
00:42:48,440 --> 00:42:51,240
Cabin crew All-New is here to provide you the best service.

852
00:42:57,640 --> 00:43:00,720
All-New will be a flight attendant at Glamorous Airline.

853
00:43:00,720 --> 00:43:03,160
So he can help you find more information.

854
00:43:03,160 --> 00:43:07,000
Wow, All-New, you're so cool.

855
00:43:08,200 --> 00:43:10,280
This uniform suits you well.

856
00:43:10,600 --> 00:43:13,800
This look of yours kills me.

857
00:43:14,680 --> 00:43:16,880
How about the other looks?

858
00:43:16,880 --> 00:43:18,240
The other looks kill me too.

859
00:43:18,440 --> 00:43:19,480
C'mon, now.

860
00:43:19,760 --> 00:43:21,120
Stop killing me with your looks!

861
00:43:22,600 --> 00:43:23,840
I'll leave this to you both.

862
00:43:24,120 --> 00:43:26,600
Of course, I won't let you down, ma'am.

863
00:43:27,040 --> 00:43:28,400
I might let you down though.

864
00:43:28,960 --> 00:43:30,000
New!

865
00:43:30,000 --> 00:43:31,040
I'm just kidding.

866
00:43:31,480 --> 00:43:32,760
You two...

867
00:43:33,640 --> 00:43:36,320
are Porn Airline's only hope.

868
00:44:02,160 --> 00:44:03,560
Hello, Miss Loukpeach.

869
00:44:16,920 --> 00:44:18,480
You don't have to scream.

870
00:44:18,480 --> 00:44:20,040
Just have a look.

871
00:44:20,360 --> 00:44:22,080
So handsome...something like that?

872
00:44:22,200 --> 00:44:24,080
New taught me.

873
00:44:26,520 --> 00:44:27,320
That's relaxing.

874
00:44:27,920 --> 00:44:28,960
Can I smell that too?

875
00:44:29,280 --> 00:44:29,960
It's so good.

876
00:44:29,960 --> 00:44:32,480
Why are we, flight attendants, have to take care of her?

877
00:44:32,560 --> 00:44:33,440
Right.

878
00:44:33,640 --> 00:44:34,800
That's true.

879
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:38,120
We serve the passengers each day and we get tired already.

880
00:44:38,120 --> 00:44:40,440
Do we have to serve...wait...that's not it.

881
00:44:40,800 --> 00:44:42,160
Right, I spoke too politely too, let's do it again.

882
00:44:42,400 --> 00:44:43,520
Can I stop running now?

883
00:44:45,480 --> 00:44:46,680
She must be really tired for sure.

884
00:45:02,240 --> 00:45:03,560
Hi, David.

885
00:45:04,120 --> 00:45:05,440
Are you flirting with my David?

886
00:45:05,440 --> 00:45:08,840
First come, first serve, Chai.

887
00:45:09,280 --> 00:45:10,800
If Chai is throwing a birthday party...

888
00:45:10,800 --> 00:45:11,800
Mr. Glam might be there.

889
00:45:11,800 --> 00:45:13,920
I'll handle tonight.

890
00:45:17,600 --> 00:45:20,960
Excuse me, 1 spicy water hyacinth, please.

891
00:45:21,360 --> 00:45:22,800
If you're bringing Larb, just the Larb, okay?

892
00:45:22,800 --> 00:45:23,600
But Blood...

893
00:45:23,720 --> 00:45:25,160
I'll go get it at that table myself!

894
00:45:26,680 --> 00:45:27,600
Madam, what are you doing?

895
00:45:27,600 --> 00:45:28,600
If I don't have it my way,

896
00:45:29,600 --> 00:45:31,120
I guess there will be some blood!
